\b \cf2 Why is this readme so dry and humour-less?
\b0 \cf0 \
Because the Moose is incomplete. In order to make it run on MacOS X, I had to remove a lot of the old features, and now this program looks so sad compared to previous ones that I just couldn't come up with anything funny to write. I'll try to improve this as the Moose gets better.\
\

