\b0  No program can ever be complete without oodles of brave testers who endanger their data and their computers (not to mention any high opinion of the programmer they may have) to bring you a bullet-proof program. All that works in this program is only due to their scrupulous examination of Mooseness. All that's broken is due to my stupidity. You can find a current list of all testers in the Moose's "About Uli's Moose" window.\
