\b \cf2 Who are you, anyway?
\b0 \cf0 \
I don't seriously think you'd ever ask this question, but I thought I'd just put it in here anyway. That little feller named Vanity who's sitting over there in the corner, trying to cure his hangover by drinking raw eggs is forcing me to do it. My name is Uli Kusterer, and I've been a huge fan of the Moose since I first heard of it. But sadly, I soon found out that nobody had done a version for System 7 or better. So I wrote my own and got in contact with Steve Halls, who let me do it. Now we're up to 10.5 and still strong and lively.\
